languages.text: {n}Челюстной аугмент Вицента легонько поскрипывает. Юноша некоторое время испытующе смотрит на свою мать и других членов семьи.{/n} "Есть кое-что, Ваша Светлость".

traits.locale_text: {n}Челюстной аугмент Вицента легонько поскрипывает. Юноша некоторое время испытующе смотрит на свою мать и других членов семьи.{/n} "Есть кое-что, Ваша Светлость".
traits.speaker: YoungGaprak

languages.text: {n}Vicent's jaw augmetic screeches slightly. The young man scrutinises his mother and other family members for a few moments.{/n} "There is something you ought to know, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

languages.text: {n}文森特下颌上的植入物发出有些刺耳的摩擦声。这个年轻人盯着他的母亲与族人看了半晌，随后开口道。{/n}“我确实有件事情需要告诉您，大人。”
languages.original_text: {n}Vicent's jaw augmetic screeches slightly. The young man scrutinises his mother and other family members for a few moments.{/n} "There is something you ought to know, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

traits.locale_text: {n}文森特下颌上的植入物发出有些刺耳的摩擦声。这个年轻人盯着他的母亲与族人看了半晌，随后开口道。{/n}“我确实有些话想说，大人。”
traits.speaker: YoungGaprak

languages.text: {n}L'augmétique mandibulaire de Vicent produit des grincements sourds tandis que le jeune homme observe sa mère et les autres membres de sa famille.{/n} « Il y a quelque chose que vous devriez savoir, Votre Seigneurie. »
languages.original_text: {n}Vicent's jaw augmetic screeches slightly. The young man scrutinises his mother and other family members for a few moments.{/n} "There is something you ought to know, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

traits.locale_text: {n}L'augmétique mandibulaire de Vicent produit des grincements sourds tandis que le jeune homme observe longuement sa mère et les autres membres de sa famille.{/n} « Il y a bien quelque chose, Votre Seigneurie. »
traits.speaker: YoungGaprak

languages.text: {n}La mandíbula aumentada de Vicent hace un ruidito. El joven observa detenidamente a su madre y a otros miembros de su familia durante unos instantes.{/n} «Hay algo que debe saber, mi{mf|lord|lady}».
languages.original_text: {n}Vicent's jaw augmetic screeches slightly. The young man scrutinises his mother and other family members for a few moments.{/n} "There is something you ought to know, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

traits.locale_text: {n}La boca de Vicent hace un ruido. El joven observa detenidamente a su madre y a otros miembros de su familia durante un rato.{/n} «Hay algo, mi{mf|lord|lady}».
traits.speaker: YoungGaprak

languages.text: {n}Vicents Kiefer-Augmentation quietscht leicht. Der junge Mann mustert eine Weile seine Mutter und die übrigen Mitglieder seiner Familie.{/n} "Es gibt etwas, was Ihr wissen solltet, Euer {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}."
languages.original_text: {n}Vicent's jaw augmetic screeches slightly. The young man scrutinises his mother and other family members for a few moments.{/n} "There is something you ought to know, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

traits.locale_text: {n}Vicents Kiefer-Augmentation quietscht leicht. Der junge Mann mustert eine Weile seine Mutter und die übrigen Mitglieder seiner Familie.{/n} "Es gibt da etwas, Euer {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}."
traits.speaker: YoungGaprak

languages.text: {n}Vicent'ın çene ogmetiği hafifçe cızırdıyor. Genç adam, annesini ve diğer hane mensuplarını bir müddet dikkatle inceliyor.{/n} "{mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri, bilmeniz gereken bir şey var."
